    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the demo version, you will dive into a vibrant world styled like clay, battle enemies in the form of animated fast food, and test yourself in a showdown with a giant mega burger! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254830/extras/91c29b89d78c30c2de45be36adf1ce5f.poster.avif?t=1734032334\" width=700 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254830/extras/91c29b89d78c30c2de45be36adf1ce5f.webm?t=1734032334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254830/extras/91c29b89d78c30c2de45be36adf1ce5f.mp4?t=1734032334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>  <br>The design of the main characters is based on a Matryoshka doll. During the game, the player will be able to change the main character by simply switching between Matryoshka dolls inside. Each hero has a unique set of skills, and by selecting the right hero during battle, you can significantly change the outcome of the fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254830/extras/c9da88af30238098652213afa4a3451b.poster.avif?t=1734032334\" width=700 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254830/extras/c9da88af30238098652213afa4a3451b.webm?t=1734032334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254830/extras/c9da88af30238098652213afa4a3451b.mp4?t=1734032334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
